          }
        }
      }
    },
    "1. After the initial setup, create another **OAuth client ID** in the same project." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "1. 初始设置完成后，在同一项目中创建另一个 **OAuth 客户端 ID**。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "2. Select **iOS** as the **Application type** and set the **Bundle ID** to '**de.manhhao.hoshi**'." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "2. 选择 **iOS** 作为**应用类型**，并将 **Bundle ID** 设为「**de.manhhao.hoshi**」。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "3. Paste the **Client ID** in the textbox below and press '**Connect Google Drive**'." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "3. 将**客户端 ID** 粘贴到下方文本框并点击「**连接 Google Drive**」。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "4. You can sync individual books by long-pressing and selecting '**Sync**'." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "4. 长按书籍并选择「**同步**」即可同步单本书。"
          }
        }
      }
